ğŸ”¹ 2. Enhanced switch Expression (Java 12+)
------------------------------------------------
    - Can be used as an expression (returns a value).
    - Supports arrow syntax (->).
    - No need for break; anymore.
    - Uses yield when you have a block with multiple statements.





